.LP
To get access to the record definitions for the structures use: 
.br
\fI-include_lib("cosTime/include/*\&.hrl")\&.\fR\&
.SH EXPORTS
.LP
.B
register(TimerEventService, CosEventCommPushConsumer, Data) -> TimerEventHandler
